            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Our Union Record</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Spirit outlines its faithfulness to the cause of restoring the Union.
                    The Spirit maintains that the Union can best be preserved on a ground of
                    compromise and that Constitutional rights of the South should be recognized. The
                    Spirit prints extracts from its own editorials to prove its dedication to the
                    Union.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
