                    <p>The membership of this conference numbers about 6, 000; Preachers traveling
                        and local, about 60; Number of Meeting Houses, 61; Number of Sabbath
                        Schools, 50; Number of Scholars, 3, 000; Amount of Missionary funds raised
                        during the year about $2500; $1160 of which were secured on Saturday
                        evening, during Conference.</p>
